# Skill-creator iteration workspaces — deliberately untracked working files
# (eval outputs, grading.json, timing.json, generated review.html, etc.).
# Without this rule, hygiene tools that run `git stash --include-untracked`
# can sweep these into stashes and a follow-up `git clean` wipes them off
# disk. The houseplant May-18 incident was caused exactly by that pattern.
# Per-skill workspaces follow the convention `<skill-name>-workspace/` as a
# sibling to the skill directory.
plugins/*/skills/*-workspace/
skills/*-workspace/

# Claude / Codex / Gemini local artifacts (never commit)
**/auth.json
**/oauth_creds.json
**/google_accounts.json
**/installation_id
**/user_id
